data.description: **BACK ON THE MARKET** Buyers cold feet is your gain! Rare concrete block home in PSJ in this price range. This home is looking for it's new owner and offers a rural feel but close to fantastic restaurants, shopping, medical plazas, parks,  awesome views of rocket launches and sunsets over the Indian River. The home sits on a corner oversized lot complete with a new fence in 2018 and a children's jungle gym in the back yard. In 2019 hurricane rated windows and slider were installed and in 2019 UV filter/light was added to the A/C system adding to air quality. Exterior of home was painted and septic pump out and inspection was done in 2023. Remodeled  around 2006, the kitchen features light Oak cabinets and stainless appliances.  Tile floor throughout, primary bath shower and raised marble top vanities. PSJ has easy access to I-95, Kennedy Space Center. and all that Brevard County has to offer!
